b'[![](../../cdshop/cdinfo.jpg)](../../cdshop/index.htm)  \n[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)\n[Previous](av044.htm)  [Next](av046.htm)\n\n* * *\n\n## VI, 21. Charm to promote the growth of hair.\n\n1\\. Of these three earths (our) earth verily is the highest. From the surface\nof these I have now plucked a remedy.  \n2\\. Thou art the most excellent of remedies, the best of plants, as Soma (the\nmoon) is the lord in the watches of the night, as Varuna (is king) among the\ngods.  \n3\\. O ye wealthy, irresistible (plants), ye do generously bestow benefits. And\nye strengthen the hair, and, moreover, promote its increase.\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: VI, 136. Charm with the plant nitatni to promote the growth of\nhair](av046.htm)\n\n'